<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>也就是说，我们是根据 item.id 找到这个 item 是属于list 数组中的哪个index索引。找到了index，就可以根据index来删除数组中的那个元素了。</p>
